            <h1>oVirt Deployment Options</h1>
            <p>The preferred way to install oVirt is by using your operating system's package manager.</p>
            <p>This page details a traditional setup where the engine and hosts are installed separately. You
                can also install a <a href="/documentation/how-to/hosted-engine/">Self-Hosted Engine setup using Cockpit.</a></p>
            <p>See the <a href="/documentation/quickstart/quickstart-guide/">Quickstart Guide</a> for full documentation
                on installing oVirt, setting up the engine and hosts, configuring storage and networking, and creating virtual machines.</p>
        </div>
