            <p>oVirt follows the <a href="https://access.redhat.com/help/browsers/">Red Hat Customer Portal Browser Support Policy</a>.
                We recommend using the latest version of the following browsers:
                <ul>
                    <li>Firefox</li>
                    <li>Chrome</li>
                    <li>Safari</li>
                    <li>Edge</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
