            <h1>Install oVirt using package manager</h1>
            <p><strong>oVirt 4.2</strong> is intended for production use and is available for the following platforms:
                <ul>
                    <li>Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.5 or later</li>
                    <li>CentOS Linux 7.5 or later</li>
                    <li>Scientific Linux 7.5 or later</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p>
                Be sure to read the <a href="/release/4.2.5/">Release Notes for oVirt 4.2.5.</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                <div class="highlight">
                    <pre class="highlight plaintext"><code># yum install https://resources.ovirt.org/pub/yum-repo/ovirt-release42.rpm</code></pre>
                </div>
            </p>
